### Update accounting slip
PUT http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/{{accountingSlipID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slipType": "SAVED",
  "businessDay": "2025-01-01",
  "accountingDatetime": "2025-01-01T11:00:00+09:00",
  "includingTaxTotalAmount": 12000,
  "paymentAmount": 12000
}

### Update accounting slip history
PUT http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/history/{{accountingSlipID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slipType": "SAVED",
  "businessDay": "2025-01-01",
  "accountingDatetime": "2025-01-01T11:30:00+09:00",
  "includingTaxTotalAmount": 11500,
  "paymentAmount": 11500
}

### Get accounting slip detail
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/{{accountingSlipID}}
Accept: application/json

### Get accounting slip detail for printing
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/{{accountingSlipID}}/printing
Accept: application/json

### Delete accounting slip
DELETE http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/{{accountingSlipID}}
Accept: application/json

### Mark slip as RETURN
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/{{accountingSlipID}}/return
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer refund",
  "disbursementAmount": 11000
}

### Daily slip statistic
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/dailySlipStatistic?companyCode=COMPANY01&businessDay=2025-01-01&orgID={{orgId}}
Accept: application/json

### Daily detail statistic
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/accountingSlips/dailyDetailStatistic?companyCode=COMPANY01&businessDay=2025-01-01&orgID={{orgId}}
Accept: application/json

